General.Name: Momentum Group AB (publ)
General.Description: Momentum Group AB (publ) supplies industrial components, industrial services, and related services to the industrial sector. It offers hydraulics, linear technology, and pneumatics products and services in to industrial companies; process valves and measuring instruments, as well as assembly, consulting, training, and service; industrial components and services, including transmission, hydraulics, and pumps; industrial supplies, such as tools, fasteners, and personal protection; flow technology solutions and products; flexible automation services; and hydraulic systems, high-pressure pumps, test pressure equipment and gas booster systems. The company also provides service, repairs, and conversions for electromechanical equipment comprising electric motors, generators, transformers and pumps, transmission products, compressors, etc.; and products and services in measurement technology. The company was founded in 1997 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
